'desc': [u'

MeeMee Powder Puff (Blue) Price: Rs.225

Baby powder is dusted on a baby’s body after bathing her to keep the skin free of unwanted moisture that can cause unpleasant rashes and irritations. When you dust the powder directly onto the skin from a container it will not fall evenly and hence a powder puff is used. The Mee Mee Powder Puff is designed to suit an infant’s delicate skin. This Powder Puff has been made with a soft acrylic puff that will help you apply the powder on your bundle of joy’s skin evenly.

The soft fur like material used in this Mee Mee Powder Puff will brush gently on your tiny tot’s skin as you apply the powder to her fragile body. The handle of the Powder Puff is made of non-toxic material and hence it is absolutely safe to be used with newborns and older children. This easy to use Mee Mee Powder Puff can be cleaned easily and the unbreakable material used will increase the longevity of the Powder Puff.

Keeping your infant safe and healthy is what every parent will strive to do from the day one. When doing so parents should make sure to keep the baby’s fingers clean as well because children tend to put their hands in their mouth quite often. Dirt can get accumulated between the nails and this can go inside the child’s mouth and stomach. To prevent this you can ensure that the baby’s nails are trimmed and kept clean all the time. The Mee Mee Safety Nail Cutter is shaped and crafted to suit an infant’s tiny fingers and toes.

Sharp edges are avoided in these Mee Mee Nail Clippers to ensure absolute safety to your baby.\xa0You can use this Mee Mee Safety Nail Cutter that meets the FDA Standards to cut the nails on your newborn’s fingers and toes with precision and care.\xa0It is ideal to cut your tiny tot’s nails when they are asleep as this will keep them calm and you will not have to manage their resistance. With this appealingly designed Mee Mee Nail Cutters you can now trim your bundle of joy’s nails without scaring them.

When it comes to cleaning your infant’s skin you will tend to be extra cautious to make sure that no spot is left without cleaning. After bathing your infant and patting her dry there could be places like the creases of the ear and the navel that needs to be dried so as to prevent infections. The Mee Mee Cotton buds with the Spiral Tips can be of great help. These cotton swabs made of 100 per cent cotton are highly absorbent and will soak up all the extra moisture from your bundle of joy’s skin.

column13: navel
